  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>As the last human on a planet ruled by robots, you have nothing left to lose. This is your final chance to avenge humanity by hacking into the system to locate the mastermind behind its destruction.</i> <br><br>You’ll need powerful programs to speed up your progress and improve your chances of reaching access nodes before being destroyed by the <strong>DoomWall</strong>. <br><br>In this 40-level, turn-based puzzle game, you'll face obstacles like bit barriers, lasers, and digital monsters, all trying to slow you down before the <strong>DoomWall</strong> catches up and forces you out of the Nexus. Don’t waste a turn—each one counts in your race to survive!<br><br>Here some examples of programs and items to use at your advantage: <br><br>Use the <strong>Quantum Grapple</strong> and the <strong>Neo Blade</strong> to get through the obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339460/extras/24d2c87e4a0742914d4cc6e72e0705e6.poster.avif?t=1732852851\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339460/extras/24d2c87e4a0742914d4cc6e72e0705e6.webm?t=1732852851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339460/extras/24d2c87e4a0742914d4cc6e72e0705e6.mp4?t=1732852851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find chips along the way to help you slowdown the DoomWall.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339460/extras/f1a4ebb61c52c0b337ae5bb4282bea12.poster.avif?t=1732852851\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339460/extras/f1a4ebb61c52c0b337ae5bb4282bea12.webm?t=1732852851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339460/extras/f1a4ebb61c52c0b337ae5bb4282bea12.mp4?t=1732852851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>As the last human on a planet ruled by robots, you have nothing left to lose. This is your final chance to avenge humanity by hacking into the system to locate the mastermind behind its destruction.</i> <br><br>You’ll need powerful programs to speed up your progress and improve your chances of reaching access nodes before being destroyed by the <strong>DoomWall</strong>. <br><br>In this 40-level, turn-based puzzle game, you'll face obstacles like bit barriers, lasers, and digital monsters, all trying to slow you down before the <strong>DoomWall</strong> catches up and forces you out of the Nexus. Don’t waste a turn—each one counts in your race to survive!<br><br>Here some examples of programs and items to use at your advantage: <br><br>Use the <strong>Quantum Grapple</strong> and the <strong>Neo Blade</strong> to get through the obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339460/extras/24d2c87e4a0742914d4cc6e72e0705e6.poster.avif?t=1732852851\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339460/extras/24d2c87e4a0742914d4cc6e72e0705e6.webm?t=1732852851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339460/extras/24d2c87e4a0742914d4cc6e72e0705e6.mp4?t=1732852851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find chips along the way to help you slowdown the DoomWall.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339460/extras/f1a4ebb61c52c0b337ae5bb4282bea12.poster.avif?t=1732852851\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.stea